{"tid":1487714,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[和平合法行動] 萬人齊心洗國旗，世界紀錄預埋你","createTime":"2019-08-19T11:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T17:14:54.000Z","uid":276716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"819ad8fbaa076b78f3f762505fce458c90862161","tid":1487714,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"據說鄰國係忌水旺火，所以燒旗只會越燒越旺。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f4V2zYR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff4V2zYR.jpg&h=6db8ec08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果國旗污糟咗，都一定要用水洗㗎喎。<br />\n<br />\n咁既然係污糟咗，桶水洗到變黑色都唔出奇，唯有再落多啲泡。<br />\n<br />\n咁為環保節約用水，香港人不如約埋一齊洗旗。<br />\n<br />\n咁洗完支旗濕笠笠， 自然要掛出嚟晾。晾晾下見到未乾淨，咪要再射啲泡上去捽。<br />\n<br />\n啲外媒見到香港人咁齊心洗旗，應該會報導下。如果有幾百幾千人一齊洗，可以申報健力士世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n以上行為應該冇犯國旗法？求解答。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔到，如果覺得有創意請幫推<br />\n<br />\nP.S<br />\n呢個post同以下新聞無關，特此澄清。<br />\n<br />\n不滿政府貪污 祕魯洗國旗抗議<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvbs.com.tw/other/383046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fother%2F383046&d=00b%2B5OzPsUCZ7nX0ilF46ze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=d8f2abf4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvbs.com.tw/other/383046</a>"},{"pid":"4fb4937905d017b397030e5edc6e166e9a6d6073","tid":1487714,"uid":159890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"咁不如集體潑墨"}]}